    "content": "<p>Software engineer with experience building scalable web platforms and data-driven products using <strong>React</strong>, <strong>Next.js</strong>, and modern frontend architectures. Experienced in developing analytics platforms, semantic data modeling tools, AI-powered search interfaces, and high-performance enterprise applications.</p>"
