            "label": ""
          },
          "description": "<ul><li><p>Designed and developed an <strong>interactive semantic data modeling interface</strong> using <strong>React Flow</strong>, enabling users to visually define tables, relationships, joins, and transformations to build semantic layers for enterprise analytics.</p></li><li><p>Implemented <strong>natural language search capabilities</strong> allowing users to query enterprise datasets in plain English, powered by semantic context graphs and structured data models to deliver accurate <strong>AI-driven insights</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Built <strong>interactive analytics and data visualization interfaces</strong>, including bar charts, dynamic filters, and metric-driven dashboards enabling <strong>self-service insights</strong> for business users.</p></li><li><p>Improved search page performance and reduced load times by migrating rendering and data handling to a <strong>client-side React architecture</strong>, enhancing responsiveness and user experience.</p></li></ul>",
          "roles": []
        },
        {
          "id": "gida-exp",
          "hidden": false,
          "company": "Gida Technologies",
          "position": "Senior Frontend Developer",
          "location": "Bangalore, India",
          "period": "March 2022 - May 2025",
          "website": {
            "url": "",
            "label": ""
          },
          "description": "<ul><li><p>Worked with enterprise clients across healthcare, insurance, and digital products building scalable web and mobile applications.</p></li><li><p>Collaborated with cross-functional teams to design performant frontend architectures and deliver production-grade applications.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Client Projects:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>HDFC ERGO Self-Help</strong>: Lead frontend developer implementing claims processing, document uploads, and insurance workflows. Integrated <strong>Strapi CMS</strong>. Tech: <strong>Next.js</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>HDFC ERGO ConveneX</strong>: Built an event management platform with admin portal, media gallery, and real-time event updates using <strong>Firebase</strong>. Tech: <strong>Next.js, Flutter</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>Antara AGEasy</strong>: Developed customer platform and admin portal including appointment scheduling, warehouse management, and recommendation engine. Improved SEO and performance using <strong>SSR</strong>, <strong>SSG</strong>, lazy loading and code splitting. Tech: <strong>Next.js, Flutter Web</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>Lyfe Apps (Lupin Digital Health)</strong>: Built healthcare apps integrating <strong>Google Fit</strong>, <strong>Apple Health</strong>, and <strong>iHealth</strong>. Implemented real-time consultations using <strong>PubNub</strong> and <strong>Jitsi</strong>. Tech: <strong>React Native, Next.js</strong>.</p></li><li><p><strong>Cubbies App</strong>: Built a children's interactive storytelling and music application using <strong>BLE</strong> connectivity to interact with a smart music box.</p></li><li><p><strong>HDFC ERGO Baltics Prototype</strong>: Developed prototype frontend demonstrating insurance purchase flows including policy selection and premium calculation.</p></li></ul>",
          "roles": []
        }
      ]
